column4: When I am trying to connect to a wireless network, the network-manager says that the device in unmanaged. Could anyone help me?
dude, you know the essid of your router?
should i just add network info by ifconfig down
type sudo iwconfig eth1 essid [ur_essid] mode managed key 1234567890
yes, but if there isn't any?
type sudo iwconfig eth1 essid [ur_essid] mode managed key 1234567890
